  <div class="border-b border-gray-700 pb-5">
    <dt class="text-purple-400 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Availability</dt>
    <dd class="text-gray-300">Regular schedule is Tuesday–Sunday at 7:30 PM. Additional tour times are offered in October, including Monday evenings and weekend matinee tours when the weather cools off.</dd>
  </div>

  <div class="border-b border-gray-700 pb-5">
    <dt class="text-purple-400 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Minimum Party Size</dt>
