  </div>

  <div class="border-b border-gray-700 pb-5">
    <dt class="text-purple-400 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Maximum Party Size</dt>
    <dd class="text-gray-300">The van accommodates 11 guests. You may book parties up to 10 online. If you need that extra seat, please <a href="{{ '/#contact' | url }}" class="text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300 underline">contact us</a> to make arrangements.</dd>
  </div>

  <div class="border-b border-gray-700 pb-5">
    <dt class="text-purple-400 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Age</dt>
    <dd class="text-gray-300">Due to tour content, we request guests be 13 and up. For younger guests, please consider our <a href="{{ '/tours/private-hearse-tour/' | url }}" class="text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300 underline">Private Hearse Tour</a>.</dd>
  </div>

  <div class="border-b border-gray-700 pb-5">
    <dt class="text-purple-400 text-xs font-semibond uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Meeting Point</dt>
    <dd class="text-gray-300">All guests meet at <strong class="text-white">Walter's Tavern, 2336 S Congress Ave, Austin, TX 78704</strong> at tour time. Arrive early if you'd like to order food or drinks before the tour. Please do not be late!</dd>
  </div>

  <div class="border-b border-gray-700 pb-5">
    <dt class="text-purple-400 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Tour Length</dt>
    <dd class="text-gray-300">Tours last approximately 3 hours.</dd>
  </div>

  <div class="border-b border-gray-700 pb-5">
    <dt class="text-purple-400 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Drinks</dt>
    <dd class="text-gray-300">We provide water, sodas, cups, bottle openers, and ice. You may bring your own alcoholic beverages — BYOB is welcome.</dd>
  </div>

  <div class="border-b border-gray-700 pb-5">
    <dt class="text-purple-400 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Clay Pit Coupon</dt>
    <dd class="text-gray-300">Each ticket includes a <strong class="text-white">2-for-1 entree coupon</strong> for the Clay Pit Restaurant — one of your spooky stops — redeemable anytime.</dd>
  </div>

  <div class="border-b border-gray-700 pb-5">
    <dt class="text-purple-400 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Gratuity</dt>
    <dd class="text-gray-300">
      Your guide works hard to provide a safe and memorable experience. Tipping is appreciated — here are some guidelines:
      <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-gray-400">
        <li>18% — Good</li>
        <li>20% — Great</li>
        <li>25% — Amazing</li>
        <li>28% — Time of your life!</li>
      </ul>
      Cash, Venmo, Cash App, and other digital payments accepted.
    </dd>
  </div>

  <div class="pb-5">
    <dt class="text-purple-400 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Cancellation Policy</dt>
    <dd class="text-gray-300">Space is limited and seats cannot be re-sold once reserved.
      <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-gray-400 list-disc list-inside">
        <li>No-shows, same-day cancellations, and cancellations with less than 48 hours notice: <strong class="text-white">no refund</strong></li>
        <li>Canceled 2–7 days before your tour: <strong class="text-white">50% refund</strong></li>
        <li>Canceled 7 or more days before your tour: <strong class="text-white">full refund</strong></li>
      </ul>
    </dd>
  </div>

</dl>

